#============================================================================
# Maven build instructions
#============================================================================
When you checkout for development, ensure you have SNAPSHOT within the pom's
version number. Any deploy without SNAPSHOT in the version number will 
attempt to deploy to the Release repository.

To build and install to your local repository, from the command line:
> mvn clean install

To build and deploy to the BRISSKit remote repository, from the command line:
> mvn clean deploy
